      <strong class='source_title'>Value of Primary Agricultural Export Commodity</strong>
    </div>

    <div class='source_body'>
      <div class='source_summary'>
        <p>Global economic growth based on the export of primary commodities and increased demand for timber and agricultural products are critical indirect drivers of deforestation and forest degradation (Kissinger et al. 2012; DeFries et al. 2010). </p>
        <p>Here we display the net export value per capita of each country’s primary agricultural commodity, as estimated from FAOSTAT data.</p>

